\cf3 \cb19 7. Out of Scope (20 items)\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19 8. Non-Functional Requirements\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19 9. Stakeholder Analysis\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19 10. Risk Register\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19 11. Success Metrics & KPIs\cf0 \cb1 \
