\cf3 \cb19   - AC2: Search matches against: manufacturer string, product string, serial number,\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     VID:PID hex, class description, machine hostname\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC3: Filter dropdown allows filtering by: All / Compatible Only / HID / Storage /\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     Audio / Video / Serial / Security Tokens / Custom\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC4: Filtered view shows which machine each matching device belongs to\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC5: "No results" state is shown with helpful message when no devices match\cf0 \cb1 \
