\cf3 \cb19   - AC3: Agent detects if vhci-hcd is available and reports capability to orchestrator\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC4: If vhci-hcd is not available, agent reports INCOMPATIBLE for client role\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     with suggestion to check LXC configuration\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC5: PVE 8.1+ `pct set <id> --dev0 /dev/bus/usb/...` method is documented\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     as alternative for direct passthrough\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19 - **Priority:** Medium\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19 - **Phase:** 2\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf3 \cb19 ---\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf3 \cb19 ### CATEGORY C: Web UI & Dashboard (US-021 to US-030)\cf0 \cb1 \
