\cf3 \cb19   - AC3: WebSocket disconnection shows "Reconnecting..." banner; reconnects\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     automatically within 30 seconds\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC4: On reconnect, full state snapshot is requested and dashboard reconciles\cf0 \cb1 \
