\
\cf3 \cb19 **US-024: Receive automated error diagnosis suggestions**\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19 - **As a** non-expert user\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19 - **I want** the system to automatically diagnose common errors and suggest fixes\cf0 \cb1 \
