\cf3 \cb19 - **Acceptance Criteria:**\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC1: Error pattern "cannot bind device: already bound" \uc0\u8594  suggestion: "Run\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     `usbip unbind -b <busid>` then try again. Another process may have bound\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     this device."\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC2: Error pattern "ENOSR / EOVERFLOW" \uc0\u8594  suggestion: "Isochronous transfer\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     overflow. This device (likely audio/video) is not suitable for USB/IP over\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     your network. Try the virtual device layer instead."\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC3: Error pattern "Connection reset by peer (104)" \uc0\u8594  suggestion: "Network\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     connection dropped. Check if the remote machine is online and if port 3240\cf0 \cb1 \
