\cf3 \cb19   - AC4: Error pattern "No such busid" \uc0\u8594  suggestion: "The device bus ID has changed\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     (it was replugged). Refresh the device list."\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC5: Error pattern "cannot create stub device" \uc0\u8594  suggestion: "The usbip-host\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     kernel module is not loaded. Run: sudo modprobe usbip-host"\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19   - AC6: Error pattern "Permission denied" \uc0\u8594  suggestion: "The agent does not have\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19     sufficient privileges. Check agent systemd service configuration."\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19 - **Priority:** High\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb19 - **Phase:** 3\cf0 \cb1 \
