## 3. COMPONENT RESPONSIBILITIES\
\
### 3.1 Agent Daemon\
\
**What it IS:**\
- A lightweight, stateless background service (Rust binary)\
- The "hands" of the system \'97 executes commands on behalf of the orchestrator\
- Reports USB device state changes to orchestrator in real time\
\
**What it IS NOT:**\
- Not a database\
- Not a policy engine\
- Not a UI component\
- Not the orchestrator\
\
**Detailed Responsibilities:**\
\
