### 3.2 Orchestration Server\
\
**What it IS:**\
- The authoritative state store for the entire USB ecosystem\
- The control plane coordinator (NOT the data plane)\
- The API gateway for the web UI\
- The policy engine\
\
**What it IS NOT:**\
- Not in the USB data path (USB/IP traffic goes agent-to-agent)\
- Not a USB driver\
- Not a device emulator\
\
**Detailed Responsibilities:**\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa80\partightenfactor0

